item.title: Philippine Food Feast
item.description: I am always a big fan of Philippine cuisine, which has similar flavor as Chinese, Spanish and Malaysian cuisines. Dishes ranges from fried fish, whole roasted pig to halo-halo. Since our car maintenance place, Firestone Complete Auto Care, is very close to Journal Square in Jersey City, my husband and I always stop by at least one Filipino restaurant while waiting. Our usual go-to-spot is Philippine Bread House. There are actually two separate restaurants/shops in the store front.
